         </fig>
      </p>
      <p>A protective grille with a 30 x 30-mm mesh is attached to the control opening in the drive station cover to prevent anyone from reaching into the metering conveyor scale. The control opening is located in the top hood of the metering conveyor scale drive station to permit the safe observation of the machineâ€™s movements during operation.</p>
      <p>When the control opening is open, there is a danger of injury, especially to the eyes.  Wear protective glasses. Keep the control opening closed except when looking in..</p>
